               <p>JOHN POWELL. I live in <placeName id="t18181028-161-crimeloc925">Playhouse-yard</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18181028-161-crimeloc925" type="placeName" value="Playhouse-yard"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18181028-161-crimeloc925" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18181028-161-off923 t18181028-161-crimeloc925"></join>. The prisoner had lodged three years with me; the articles stated in the indictment were let to her with the lodging. On the 8th of September she left, and I missed them.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18181028-161-person1104">
                  LEONARD 
                  MATHEWS
               <interp inst="t18181028-161-person1104" type="surname" value="MATHEWS"></interp>
