                     <interp inst="t18181028-161-person1104" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . My father is a pawnbroker, and lives in Whitecross-street. A woman pledged a fender with us.</p>
               <p>RICHARD FALLSHAW. I am an officer. On the 10th of October I took the prisoner, and found the duplicates of the property on her.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18181028-161-person1105">
                  JOHN 
                  BARRAT
               <interp inst="t18181028-161-person1105" type="surname" value="BARRAT"></interp>
